Mapon GO 2021 is a new and improved version of the Mapon driver mobile application and is available to all registered Mapon platform users. It's still at an early stage of development and offers only a fraction of the features currently available on Mapon GO. However, we're expecting to expand the functionality of Mapon GO 2021 in the future. What's more, the new app already offers such added benefits as GPS tracking, as well as enhanced overall application speed and design for better user experience.     
The Mapon GO 2021 application is an effective tool capable of improving overall business efficiency. It gives the opportunity for drivers to communicate and exchange important information with the back-office in a digitised space. Less paper, faster communication, easy information access and more!

 FEATURES:
* Dashboard - for easy overview and access to relevant information;
* Messaging - for keeping in touch with the back office, forwarding tasks and making sure no files, orders or pictures go missing;
* Mobile tracking - provides built-in mobile tracker functionality; 
* Route history - a complete log with all of the driver's previous travels;
* Settings - for easy set-up and customisation;
* Login.

The next generation parking app, equipped with innovative features and an exclusive Smart Parking Network is now live. Are you looking for a parking space or do you want to rent yours out? Vicky is here for you.

By connecting people with our Vicky parking spaces, Vicky prevents parking capacity in inner cities from being unused. Join the community and get exclusive access to our Smart Parking Network, or rent out your unused parking space via our platform.

Features in the app:
- Park direct at Vicky parking spots (with credit card);
- Book and reserve a parking spot for guaranteed parking (with credit card & iDeal);
- Travel safely and park your vehicle entirely contactless at the majority of the Vicky locations;
- Search for parking spots close to your destination;
- Get personal travel advice via our "Last Mile Service" using Uber, public transport or on foot to your destination;
- Add multiple vehicles to your account, free of charge;
- Entrance & exit instructions for every Vicky location;
- Subscribe to a fixed parking space at one of our locations;
- Rent out your own parking space, and always determine your own price and availability;
- Flawless Parking Management via our app and easy to integrate with our software in the cloud.

Vicky is developed by people who believe in the possibilities of cities and their inhabitants. The best results are achieved within communities when we all contribute to a common goal. Our goal is to provide a sustainable solution to the structural parking problems in our cities.

